<b><it>Blood on Wolf Mountain</it></b>, also known as <b><it>The Wolf Hill</it></b>, <b><it>Bloodbath in Langshan</it></b>, and <b><it>Bloodshed on Wolf Mountain</it></b>, is a <creation wordnetid="103129123" confidence="0.8">
<artifact wordnetid="100021939" confidence="0.8">
<art wordnetid="102743547" confidence="0.8">
<link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../791/10791.xml">
Chinese film</link></art>
</artifact>
