</act>
</conflict>
</event>
</battle>
</group_action>
</military_action>
 in 1931. The film was produced by the <company wordnetid="108058098" confidence="0.8">
<institution wordnetid="108053576" confidence="0.8">
<link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../581/4575581.xml">
